{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "648b5a65417cc3fb48d662c3", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 3, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 210, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fec2b295b085ab6eb8d"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "615d92ebde3d91842a5cf7e6", "title": "JEE Main 2018 (15 Apr Shift 2 Online)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "A man in a car at location Q on a straight highway is moving with speed $\\mathrm{v}$. He decides to reach a point $P$ in a field at a distance $d$ from highway (point $M$ ) as shown in the figure.Speed of the car in the field is half to that on the highway. What should be the distance RM, so that the time taken to reach $P$ is minimum?\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/KAO7CMAojPHVxeDrpH3zszTdEUpI7RzGaJ04e_umNxo.original.fullsize.png\"><br>", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "aY1Eq", "text": "\n$\\frac{\\mathrm{d}}{\\sqrt{3}}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "9kEhG", "text": "\n$\\frac{\\mathrm{d}}{2}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "Y0pmN", "text": "\n$\\frac{\\mathrm{d}}{\\sqrt{2}}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "BFfDt", "text": "\n$\\mathrm{d}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "Let the car turn of the highway at a distance ' $x$ ' from the point $\\mathrm{M}$. So, $\\mathrm{RM}=x$ And if speed of car in field is $v$, then time taken by the car to cover the distance $Q R=$ $Q M-x$ on the highway,\n$$\nt_1=\\frac{Q M-x}{2 v}\n$$\nTime taken to travel the distance ' $R P^{\\prime}$ in the field\n$$\nt_2=\\frac{\\sqrt{d^2+x^2}}{v}\n$$\nTotal time elapsed to move the car from $Q$ to $P$\n$$\nt=t_1+t_2=\\frac{Q M-x}{2 v}+\\frac{\\sqrt{d^2+x^2}}{v}\n$$\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/HSgVqp8OOw0Ou6BQSpIKVgCCI_WMJIR4xccTk9PNI70.original.fullsize.png\"><br>\n$$\n\\text { or } x=\\frac{d}{\\sqrt{2^2-1}}=\\frac{d}{\\sqrt{3}}\n$$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ35422210", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616023b19c52e0f28ddb0775", "616023b0de8166998bc42c6d", "616023af43c51275f749f558", "61964c73d9833a69946df6f2", "61e7bd6f3bf0edf6b5de3a0b", "61964c746f9d7c1ee88dadf2", "616023aeab028caf34f8696e", "61c089866e775b4063ccd8a4", "616023b0785fa46404399f50", "61bb820e7ded9395491665d7", "629109efb7e6d88372f6f913", "629f390d082fd4386414ddf1", "629f3a923db4e88dec15f6fb", "629621249a4459f8a4446124", "64eb06be3118f713ecfef063", "66d58535a75f05ee8564f537", "67921d621d5b5072da5e9a97", "67fdff56378e1624ea7b6a62", "6809202e3a10446a207fdf09"], "cpyqbExams": ["615f0e999476412f48314daf", "616059af0283de43c87e3e23"]}}